Name: Tony Slavin Ladies and Gentlemens Salon
Description: If you haven't heard the song Penny Lane by the Beatles, you'll have a hard time figuring out what we're talking about. "In Penny Lane there is a barber showing photographs, Of every head he's had the pleasure to know". Covered in pictures of the beatles getting their famous haircut, this place is a big tourist destination for music lovers visiting Liverpool.
